{"tid":2418254,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"又有傳銷狗打電話過黎叫我交智商稅","createTime":"2021-02-22T12:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T15:01:33.000Z","uid":317202,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd549c0b88a3a619b89d2cf09a3163b2375862d","tid":2418254,"uid":317202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvDCOdr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvDCOdr.png&h=0d534252&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqsPEj6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqsPEj6.png&h=1f0a3e1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個月前有個女仔打黎，話阻我一分鍾做問卷<br />\n我聽到把聲幾甜就應承左，佢問我做咩行業，收入咩range，同唔同意年假加到21日，之後就收左線<br />\n<br />\n琴日打電話黎話我中左獎，送我外國酒店5日4夜，國家自己揀，因為疫情關係，個套票有一年時間，咩時候去都得，再送多盒口罩比我，但係第二日6:00pm要去佢尖沙咀公司聽講座。<br />\n我應承左，但係即時上網查個電話號碼發現原來係個天仙局，所以放左佢飛機<br />\n<br />\n然後佢地不停炸鳩我，block 完又換其他Number <br />\n屌！<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">傳銷狗食屎啦</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8df10ef2d340a1f34232e0cd90cf4bc426735a51","tid":2418254,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395813f51738d2d8a91446a5aeafbcc0e267b65a","tid":2418254,"uid":317202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8df10ef2d340a1f34232e0cd90cf4bc426735a51","tid":2418254,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48fe5bf3a357144d454282868210fb29ae030d6e","tid":2418254,"uid":311002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:01:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09ef1b6dadf92f7137abc1e298a3d3b67ca1b19a","tid":2418254,"uid":245713,